Description:
    Generates an admin layout styled like 37 Signals applications, ready to use
    with decent looking forms using a custom form builder
    
Usage:
    If you do not pass any arguments, the site name will default to "Your Site" and the Hue of the header bar/links will default to 92 degrees

Examples:
    script/generate andy_admin
    script/generate andy_admin "My Site Name"
    script/generate andy_admin "My Site Name" 232
